                {
                    "name": "Crystalline Dust Form",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "The axiomite shifts between its humanoid form and that of a cloud of crystalline dust in which strange symbols and equations flash. In this form it gains a fly Speed of 40 feet and can fit through even tiny apertures, similarly to <a aonid=\"129\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>gaseous form</i></a>. It can cast spells, but it can\u2019t make melee or ranged attacks in this state. It can return to its humanoid form by using this action while in crystalline dust form.",
